    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='152:178'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-1a' );" name="009-1a" class="pb">[009-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='178:186'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='186:195'>　大戴禮記卷九</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='195:216'>　　　　　　　　　　　　　漢　戴德　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='216:239'>　千乗第六十七<span class='krp-note'>案各本改作六/十八今訂正</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='239:262'>　四代第六十八<span class='krp-note'>案各本改作六/十九今訂正</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='262:285'>　虞戴徳第六十九<span class='krp-note'>案各本改作/七十今訂正</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='285:307'>　誥志第七十<span class='krp-note'>案各本改作七/十一今訂正</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='307:313'>　　千乗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='313:339'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-1b' );" name="009-1b" class="pb">[009-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='339:362'>公曰千乗之國受命于天子通其四疆教其書社修其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='362:395'>灌廟<span class='krp-note'>案修各本訛作循/今從高安本方本</span>建其宗主設其四佐列其五官</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='395:418'>處其朝市為仁如何子曰不仁國不化公曰何如之謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='418:441'>仁子曰不淫于色子曰立妃設如太廟然乃中治中治</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='441:464'>不相陵不相陵斯庶嬪遧遧則事上靜靜斯潔信在中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='464:487'>朝大夫必慎以恭出㑹謀事必敬以慎言長幼小大必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='487:518'>中度此國家之所以崇也立子設如宗社<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱如/字今從楊本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='518:545'><span class='krp-note'>方/本</span>宗社先示威威明顯見辨爵集徳是以母弟官子咸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='545:571'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-2a' );" name="009-2a" class="pb">[009-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='571:594'>有臣志莫敢援于外大夫中婦私謁不行此所以使五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='594:625'>官治執事正也<span class='krp-note'>案正各本作/政今從方本</span>夫政以教百姓百姓齊以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='625:648'>嘉善故蠱佞不生此之謂良民國有道則民昌此國家</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='648:671'>之所以大遂也卿設如大門大門顯美小大尊卑中度</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='671:694'>開明閉幽内禄出災以順天道近者閑焉遠者稽焉君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='694:725'>發禁宰受而行之<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱受/字今從楊本</span>以時通于地散布于小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='725:754'>理<span class='krp-note'>案理方/本作治</span>天之災祥地寳豐省及民共饗其禄共任其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='754:777'>災此國家之所以和也國有四輔輔卿也卿設如四體</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='777:803'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-2b' );" name="009-2b" class="pb">[009-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='803:826'>毋易事毋假名毋重食凡事尚賢進能使知事爵不世</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='826:857'>能官之不愆<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱官/字今從楊本</span>凡民戴名以能食力以時成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='857:880'>以事立此所以使民讓也民咸孝弟而安讓此以怨省</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='880:911'>而亂不作也此國家之所以長也<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱家/字今從方本</span>下無用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='911:934'>則國家富上有義則國家治長有禮則民不爭立有神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='934:964'>則國家敬兼而愛之則民無怨心以為典令<span class='krp-note'>案各本訛/作以為無</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='964:1001'><span class='krp-note'>命今從/方本</span>則民不偷<span class='krp-note'>案盛徳篇云無度/量則小者偷惰</span>昔者先王本此六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1001:1032'>者而樹之徳此國家之所以茂也<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱之/字今從方本</span>設其四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1032:1058'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-3a' );" name="009-3a" class="pb">[009-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1058:1086'>佐而官之司徒典春以教民之不則治不若不令<span class='krp-note'>案治/各本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1086:1115'><span class='krp-note'>訛作時今/從方本</span>成長幼老疾孤寡以時通于四疆有闔而不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1115:1138'>通有煩而不治則民不樂生不利衣食凡民之藏貯以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1138:1171'>及山川之神明加于民者發圖功謀<span class='krp-note'>案圖字從劉本訂/正他本訛作國下</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1171:1202'><span class='krp-note'>舊注一作同/乃校書者語</span>齋戒必敬㑹時必節日厯巫祝執伎以守</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1202:1229'>官俟命而作祈王年禱民命及畜榖蜚征庶虞百草<span class='krp-note'>案/各</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1229:1259'><span class='krp-note'>本脱百字/今從方本</span>方春三月緩施生育動作百物于時有事享</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1259:1282'>于皇祖皇考朝孤子八人以成春事司馬司夏以教士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1282:1308'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-3b' );" name="009-3b" class="pb">[009-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1308:1331'>車甲凡士執伎論功修四衞强股肱質射御才武聰慧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1331:1362'>治衆長卒可以為儀綴于國<span class='krp-note'>案可各本訛作/所今從楊本</span>出可以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1362:1389'>率誘于軍旅四方諸侯之遊士國中賢餘秀與閱焉<span class='krp-note'>案/與</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1389:1419'><span class='krp-note'>各本訛作興/今從方本</span>方夏三月養長秀蕃庶物于時有事享于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1419:1442'>皇祖皇考爵士之有慶者七人以成夏事司寇司秋以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1442:1465'>聽獄訟治民之煩亂執權變民中凡民之刑萌本以安</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1465:1501'>閒<span class='krp-note'>案之下各本衍不字萌訛/作□安訛作要今從楊本</span>作起不敬以欺惑憧愚作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1501:1529'>于財賄六畜五榖曰盜誘居室家及幼子曰不義<span class='krp-note'>案此/六字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1529:1555'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-4a' );" name="009-4a" class="pb">[009-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1555:1588'><span class='krp-note'>各本訛作有君子曰/義五字今從方本</span>子女專曰妖飭五兵及木石曰賊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1588:1618'>以中情出小曰間大曰講<span class='krp-note'>案講當作構/或古通用</span>利辭以亂屬曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1618:1641'>讒以財投長曰貸凡犯天子之禁陳刑制辟以追罔民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1641:1672'>之不率上教者<span class='krp-note'>案罔各本作/國今從楊本</span>夫是故一家三夫道行三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1672:1695'>人餘食哀樂平無獄方秋三月收斂以時于時有事嘗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1695:1718'>新于皇祖皇考食農夫九人以成秋事司空司冬以制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1718:1741'>度制地事準揆山林規表衍沃畜水行衰濯浸以節四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1741:1764'>時之事治地遠近以任民力以節民食太古食壯之食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1764:1790'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-4b' );" name="009-4b" class="pb">[009-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1790:1813'>攻老之事公曰功事不少而餱糧不多乎子曰太古之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1813:1836'>民秀長以壽者食也在今之民羸醜以胔者事也太古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1836:1868'>無游民食節事時民各安其居樂其官<span class='krp-note'>案各本訛作宫/下又加室字今</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1868:1903'><span class='krp-note'>從楊/本</span>服事信上上下交信地移民聚<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱聚/字今從方本</span>在今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1903:1926'>之世上治不平民治不和百姓不安其居不樂其官老</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1926:1949'>疾用財壯狡用力于兹民游薄事貪食于兹民憂古者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1949:1972'>殷書為成男成女名屬升于公門此以氣食得節作事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1972:2003'>得時民勸有功<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱民/字今從楊本</span>夏服君事不及暍冬服君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='2003:2029'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-5a' );" name="009-5a" class="pb">[009-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='2029:2060'>事不及凍是故年榖順成<span class='krp-note'>案順各本訛作/不今從方本</span>天之饑饉道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='2060:2083'>無殣者在今之世男女屬散名不升于公門此以氣食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='2083:2114'>不節作事不時<span class='krp-note'>案時各本作/成今從楊本</span>天之饑饉于時委民不得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='2114:2137'>以疾死是故立民之居必于中國之休地因寒暑之和</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='2137:2160'>六畜育焉五榖宜焉辨輕重制剛柔和五味以節食時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='2160:2183'>事東辟之民曰夷精以僥至于大遠有不火食者矣南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='2183:2206'>辟之民曰蠻信以朴至于大遠有不火食者矣西辟之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='2206:2229'>民曰戎勁以剛至于大遠有不火食者矣北辟之民曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='2229:2255'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-5b' );" name="009-5b" class="pb">[009-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='2255:2278'>狄肥以戾至于大遠有不火食者矣及中國之民曰五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2278:2311'>方之民咸有安居和味<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱咸字居/訛作民今從楊本</span>咸有實用利</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2311:2334'>器知通之信令之及量地度居有城郭立朝市地以度</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2334:2357'>邑邑以度民以觀安危距封後利先慮乆固依固可守</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2357:2386'>為奥可乆<span class='krp-note'>案奥隩/古通用</span>能節四時之事霜露時降方冬三月</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2386:2409'>草木落庶虞藏五榖必入于倉于時有事蒸于皇祖皇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2409:2436'>考息國老六人以成冬事民咸知孤寡之必不末也<span class='krp-note'>案/末</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2436:2468'><span class='krp-note'>字他本訛作未/今從劉本楊本</span>咸知有大功之必進等也咸知用勞力</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2468:2494'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-6a' );" name="009-6a" class="pb">[009-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2494:2523'>之必以時息也推而内之水火<span class='krp-note'>案内納/古通用</span>入也弗之顧矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2523:2552'>而况有强適在前<span class='krp-note'>案適敵/古通用</span>有君長正之者乎公曰善哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2552:2558'>　　四代</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2558:2581'>公曰四代之政刑論其明者可以為法乎子曰何哉四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2581:2604'>代之政刑皆可法也公曰以我行之其可乎子曰否不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2604:2627'>可臣願君之立知而以觀聞也四代之政刑君若用之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2627:2650'>則緩急將有所不節不節君將約之約之卒將棄法棄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2650:2673'>法是無以為國家也公曰巧匠輔繩而斲胡為其棄法</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2673:2699'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-6b' );" name="009-6b" class="pb">[009-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2699:2729'>也子曰心未之度習未之狎<span class='krp-note'>案未之楊本/皆作之未</span>此以數踰而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2729:2752'>棄法也夫規矩準繩鈞衡此昔者先王之所以為天下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2752:2775'>也小以及大近以知遠今日行之可以知古可以察今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2775:2798'>其此耶水火金木土榖此謂六府廢一不可進一不可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2798:2821'>民竝用之今日行之可以知古可以察今其此耶昔夏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2821:2855'>商之未興也伯夷謂此三常之眇<span class='krp-note'>案三常又見虞戴徳/篇各本常訛作帝因</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2855:2883'><span class='krp-note'>又訛為/二帝</span>公曰長國治民恒幹論政之大體以教民辨厯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2883:2906'>大道以時地性興民之陽徳以教民事上服周室之典</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2906:2932'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-7a' );" name="009-7a" class="pb">[009-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2932:2955'>以順事天子修政勤禮以交諸侯大節無廢小眇其後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2955:2986'>乎<span class='krp-note'>案小各本訛作/少今從程本</span>子曰否不可後也詩云東有開明于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2986:3018'>時雞三號以興庶虞動<span class='krp-note'>案各本重庶虞/二字今從楊本</span>蜚征作嗇民執</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='3018:3041'>功百草咸淳地傾水流之是以天子盛服朝日于東堂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='3041:3064'>以教敬示威于天下也是以祭祀昭有神明燕食昭有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='3064:3087'>慈愛宗廟之事昭有義率禮朝廷昭有五官無廢甲胄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='3087:3110'>之戒昭果毅以聽天子曰崩諸侯曰薨大夫曰卒士曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='3110:3141'>不禄庻人曰死昭哀哀慶無失節<span class='krp-note'>案慶各本訛作/愛今從方本</span>是以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='3141:3167'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-7b' );" name="009-7b" class="pb">[009-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='3167:3190'>父慈子孝兄愛弟敬此昔先王之所先施于民也君而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='3190:3213'>後此則為國家失本矣公曰善哉子察教我也子曰鄉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='3213:3236'>也君之言善執國之節也君先眇而後善中備以君之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='3236:3267'>言<span class='krp-note'>案之各本訛作/子今從楊本</span>可以知古可以察今奐然而與民壹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='3267:3298'>始<span class='krp-note'>案與各本訛作/興今從方本</span>公曰是非吾言也吾一聞于師也子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='3298:3321'>吁焉其色曰嘻君行道矣公曰道耶子曰道也公曰吾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='3321:3344'>未能知人未能取人子曰君何為不觀器視才公曰視</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='3344:3367'>可明乎子曰可以表儀公曰願學之子曰平原大藪瞻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='3367:3393'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-8a' );" name="009-8a" class="pb">[009-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='3393:3421'>其草之高豐茂者必有怪鳥獸居之且草可財也<span class='krp-note'>案財/材古</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='3421:3456'><span class='krp-note'>通/用</span>如艾而夷之<span class='krp-note'>案艾刈古通用/夷薙古通用</span>其地必宜五榖高山多</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='3456:3479'>林必有怪虎豹蕃孕焉深淵大川必有蛟龍焉民亦如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='3479:3502'>之君察之此可以見器見才矣公曰吾猶未也子曰羣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='3502:3525'>然戚然頤然睪然踖然柱然抽然首然僉然湛然淵淵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3525:3548'>然淑淑然齊齊然節節然穆穆然皇皇然見才色脩聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3548:3580'>不視聞怪物怪命不改志<span class='krp-note'>案怪命各本作/恪命今從楊本</span>舌不更氣君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3580:3603'>見之舉也得之取也有事事也事必與食食必與位無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3603:3629'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-8b' );" name="009-8b" class="pb">[009-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3629:3652'>相越踰昔虞舜天徳嗣堯取相十有六人如此公曰嘻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3652:3675'>美哉子道廣矣吾恐惽而不能用也何以哉子曰由徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3675:3711'>徑徑<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱子字下五字訛在/子道廣矣之下今從方本</span>公曰請問圖徳何尚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3711:3734'>子曰聖知之華也知仁之實也仁信之器也信義之重</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3734:3757'>也義利之本也委利生孽公曰嘻言之至也道天地以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3757:3780'>民輔之聖人何尚子曰有天徳有地徳有人徳此謂三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3780:3803'>徳三徳率行乃有陰陽陽曰徳隂曰刑公曰善哉再聞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3803:3826'>此矣陽徳何出子曰陽徳出禮禮出刑刑出慮慮則節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3826:3852'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-9a' );" name="009-9a" class="pb">[009-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3852:3875'>事于近而揚聲于遠公曰善哉載事何以子曰徳以監</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3875:3898'>位位以充局局以觀功功以養民民于此乎上公曰禄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3898:3921'>不可後乎子曰食為味味為氣氣為志發志為言發言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3921:3944'>定名名以出信信載義而行之禄不可後也公曰所謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3944:3967'>民與天地相參者何謂也子曰天道以視地道以履人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3967:3990'>道以稽廢一曰失統恐不長饗國公愀然其色子曰君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3990:4021'>藏玉惟慎用之惟慎<span class='krp-note'>案惟各本訛作/雖今從方本</span>敬而勿愛民亦如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='4021:4044'>之執事無貳五官有差喜無竝愛卑無加尊淺無測深</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='4044:4070'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-9b' );" name="009-9b" class="pb">[009-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='4070:4093'>小無招大此謂楣機楣機賓薦不䝉昔舜徴薦此道于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='4093:4116'>堯堯親用之不亂上下公曰請問民徴子曰無以為也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='4116:4139'>難行公曰願學之幾必能子曰貪于味不讓妨于政願</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='4139:4162'>富不乆妨于政慕寵假貴妨于政治民惡衆妨于政為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='4162:4185'>父不慈妨于政為子不孝妨于政大縱耳目妨于政好</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='4185:4212'>色失志妨于政好見小利妨于政變從無節妨于政<span class='krp-note'>案/各</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='4212:4243'><span class='krp-note'>本脱此三字/今從高安本</span>撓弱不立妨于政剛毅犯神妨于政鬼神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='4243:4266'>過節妨于政幼勿與衆克勿與比依勿與謀放勿與游</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='4266:4293'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-10a' );" name="009-10a" class="pb">[009-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='4293:4324'>徼勿與事臣聞之弗薦<span class='krp-note'>案薦各本訛作/慶今從楊本</span>非事君也君聞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='4324:4356'>之弗用以亂厥徳臣將薦其簡者<span class='krp-note'>案薦各本亦訛/作慶今從楊本</span>蓋人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='4356:4379'>有可知者焉貌色聲衆有美焉必有美質在其中者矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='4379:4402'>貌色聲衆有惡焉必有惡質在其中者矣此皆伯夷之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='4402:4442'>所後出也<span class='krp-note'>案皆各本訛作/者今從高安本</span>子曰伯夷曰<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱曰/字今從楊本</span>建</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='4442:4473'>國建政修國修政<span class='krp-note'>案上修字下舊注一/作循乃校書者語</span>公曰善哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='4473:4480'>　　虞戴徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='4480:4503'>公曰昔有虞戴徳何以深慮何及高舉安取子曰君已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='4503:4530'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-10b' );" name="009-10b" class="pb">[009-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='4530:4565'>聞之<span class='krp-note'>案已各本作/以今從楊本</span>惟丘無以更也君之聞而未成也<span class='krp-note'>案/而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='4565:4604'><span class='krp-note'>各本作如/今從方本</span>黄帝慕修之<span class='krp-note'>案修下舊注一作/循乃校書者語</span>曰明法于天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='4604:4639'>明<span class='krp-note'>案此下各本衍一開字楊/本重一明字今從方本</span>施教于民行此以上明于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='4639:4672'>天化也開物畢起<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱開字畢/訛作必今從方本</span>是故民聽命而弗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='4672:4703'>改也<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱聽/字今從方本</span>公曰善哉以天教于民可以班乎子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='4703:4733'>曰可哉雖可而弗由此上知所以行斧鉞也<span class='krp-note'>案此下各/本衍以字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='4733:4761'><span class='krp-note'>今從/方本</span>父之于子天也君之于臣天也有子不事父有臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='4761:4784'>不事君是非反天而倒行耶故有子不事父不順有臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4784:4811'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-11a' );" name="009-11a" class="pb">[009-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4811:4834'>不事君必刃順天作刑地生庶物是故聖人之教于民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4834:4865'>也率天而祖地<span class='krp-note'>案而各本作/如今從方本</span>能用民徳是以高舉不過</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4865:4888'>天深慮不過地質知而好仁能用民力此以三常之禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4888:4911'>明而名不蹇禮失則壞名失則惽是故上古不諱正天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4911:4934'>名也天子之官四通正地事也天子御珽諸侯御荼大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4934:4957'>夫服笏正民徳也斂此三者而一舉之戴天履地以順</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4957:4980'>民事天子告朔于諸侯率天道而敬行之以示威于天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4980:5015'>下也諸侯内貢于天子<span class='krp-note'>案内納/古通用</span>率名斆地實也<span class='krp-note'>案斆效/古通用</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='5015:5042'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-11b' );" name="009-11b" class="pb">[009-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='5042:5065'>是以不至必誅諸侯相見卿為介以其教士畢行使仁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='5065:5088'>守㑹朝于天子天子以嵗二月為壇于東郊建五色設</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='5088:5120'>五兵具五味陳六律奏五聲<span class='krp-note'>案律下各本衍/品字今從方本</span>聽明教置</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='5120:5151'>離抗大侯規鵠豎物<span class='krp-note'>案豎各本訛作/堅今從楊本</span>九卿佐三公三公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='5151:5174'>佐天子天子踐位諸侯各以其屬就位乃升諸侯之教</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='5174:5206'>士<span class='krp-note'>案各本重諸侯/二字今從方本</span>教士執弓挾矢揖讓而升履物以射</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='5206:5238'>其心志端<span class='krp-note'>案各本訛作其地/心端今從方本</span>色容正時以斆伎時有慶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='5238:5261'>以地不時有讓以地天下之有道也有天子存國之有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='5261:5288'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-12a' );" name="009-12a" class="pb">[009-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='5288:5311'>道也君得其正家之不亂也有仁父存是故聖人之教</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='5311:5334'>于民也以其近而見者稽其遠而明者天事曰明地事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='5334:5365'>曰昌人事曰樂<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱樂/字今從方本</span>比兩以慶違此三者謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='5365:5388'>愚民愚民曰姦姦必誅是以天下平而國家治民亦無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='5388:5417'>貸居小不約居大則治衆則集寡則繆<span class='krp-note'>案繆穆/古通用</span>祀則得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='5417:5440'>福以征則服此惟官民之上徳也公曰三代之相授必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='5440:5463'>更制典物道乎子曰否猷徳保保惽乎前以小繼大變</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='5463:5494'>民視也<span class='krp-note'>案視各本作/示今從方本</span>公曰善哉子之察教我也子曰丘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='5494:5521'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-12b' );" name="009-12b" class="pb">[009-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='5521:5544'>于君惟無言言必盡于他人則否公曰教他人則如何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='5544:5572'>子曰否丘則不能昔啇老彭及仲傀<span class='krp-note'>案即/仲虺</span>政之教大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='5572:5595'>官之教士技之教庻人揚則抑抑則揚綴以徳行不任</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='5595:5626'>以言任庻人以言<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱任/字今從楊本</span>猶以夏后氏之袝懷袍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='5626:5658'>褐也<span class='krp-note'>案朱本沈本脱/袍字今從各本</span>行不越境公曰善哉我則問政子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='5658:5681'>事教我子曰君問已參黄帝之制制之大禮也公曰先</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='5681:5704'>聖之道斯為美乎子曰斯為美雖有美者必偏屬于斯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='5704:5735'>昭天之福迎之以祥作地之穡<span class='krp-note'>案穯各本訛作/福今從方本</span>制之以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='5735:5762'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-13a' );" name="009-13a" class="pb">[009-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='5762:5777'>昌興民之徳守之以長公曰善哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='5777:5783'>　　誥志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='5783:5806'>公曰誥志無荒以㑹民義齋戒必敬㑹時必節犧牲必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='5806:5829'>全齊盛必潔上下禋祀外内無失節其可以省怨遠災</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='5829:5852'>乎子曰丘未知其可以省怨也公曰然則何以事神子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='5852:5883'>曰以禮㑹時夫民見其禮則上不援<span class='krp-note'>案不各本訛作/下今從楊本</span>不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='5883:5914'>援則樂<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱不/字今從楊本</span>樂斯無憂此以怨省而亂不作也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='5914:5946'><span class='krp-note'>案此以各本訛作/以此今從楊本</span>夫禮㑹其四時四孟四季五牲五榖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='5946:5973'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-13b' );" name="009-13b" class="pb">[009-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='5973:6005'>順至必時其節<span class='krp-note'>案此下各本衍/也字今從楊本</span>丘未知其可以遠災也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='6005:6037'><span class='krp-note'>案此下各本衍/為字今從楊本</span>公曰然則為此何以子曰知仁合則天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='6037:6082'>地成天地成則庶物時庶物時則民財<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2394' title='KR2394' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2394.png'/><span class='krp-note'>案<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2394' title='KR2394' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2394.png'/>字從楊/本各本訛作</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='6082:6121'><span class='krp-note'>敬下有一作欲三/字乃校書者語</span>民財<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2394' title='KR2394' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2394.png'/>以時作時作則節事節事以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='6121:6153'>動衆則有極<span class='krp-note'>案各本重動衆/二字今從楊本</span>有極以使民則勸勸則有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='6153:6183'>功有功則無怨無怨則嗣世乆世乆惟聖人<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱/下世乆二</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='6183:6211'><span class='krp-note'>字今從/楊本</span>是故政以勝衆非以陵衆衆以勝事非以傷事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='6211:6234'>事以靖民非以徴民故地廣而民衆非以為災長之禄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='6234:6261'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-14a' );" name="009-14a" class="pb">[009-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='6261:6293'>也丘聞周太史曰政不率天<span class='krp-note'>案此下各本衍/下字今從楊本</span>不由人則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='6293:6316'>凡事易壞而難成虞史伯夷曰明孟也幽幼也明幽雌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='6316:6339'>雄也雌雄迭興而順至正之統也日歸于西起明于東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='6339:6369'>月歸于東起明于西虞夏之厯建正于孟春<span class='krp-note'>案建正各/本訛作正</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='6369:6404'><span class='krp-note'>建今從晉/志所引</span>于時冰泮發蟄百草權輿瑞雉無釋<span class='krp-note'>案史記/作百草</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='6404:6448'><span class='krp-note'>奮興秭/鳺先<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1485' title='KR1485' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1485.png'/></span>物乃嵗俱生于東次<span class='krp-note'>案各本訛作/以今從楊本</span>順四時卒于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='6448:6479'>冬方<span class='krp-note'>案各本訛作/萬今從楊本</span>于時雞三號卒明載于青色撫十二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='6479:6502'>月節卒于丑日月成嵗厯再閏以順天道此謂虞汁月</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='6502:6529'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-14b' );" name="009-14b" class="pb">[009-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='6529:6561'><span class='krp-note'>案謂下各本衍/嵗字今從楊本</span>天曰作明日與維天是戴地曰作昌日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='6561:6593'>與維地是事人曰作樂日與維民是嬉<span class='krp-note'>案三日字各本/訛作曰今從袁</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='6593:6629'><span class='krp-note'>本楊本/方本</span>民之動能不遠厥事民之妃色<span class='krp-note'>案妃各本訛作/悲今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='6629:6652'>不遠厥徳此謂表裏時合物之所生而蕃昌之道如此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='6652:6675'>天生物地養物物備興而時用常節曰聖人主祭于天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='6675:6698'>曰天子天子崩步于四川伐于四山卒葬曰帝天作仁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='6698:6721'>地作富人作治樂治不倦財富時節是故聖人嗣則治</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='6721:6744'>文王治以俟時湯治以伐亂禹治以移衆衆服以立天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='6744:6771'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-15a' );" name="009-15a" class="pb">[009-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='6771:6794'>下堯貴以樂治時舉舜舜治以徳使力在國統民而恕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='6794:6833'><span class='krp-note'>案而各本作/如今從方本</span>在家撫官如國<span class='krp-note'>案如各本作/而今從方本</span>安之勿變勸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='6833:6864'>之勿沮民咸廢惡而進良<span class='krp-note'>案而各本亦作/如今從方本</span>上誘善而行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='6864:6887'>罰百姓盡于仁而遂安之此古之明制之治天下也仁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='6887:6910'>者為聖貴次力次美次射御次古之治天下者必聖人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='6910:6944'>聖人有國則日月不食星辰不孛<span class='krp-note'>案孛各本訛作勃上/又衍隕字今從高安</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='6944:6975'><span class='krp-note'>本/</span>海不運河不滿溢川澤不竭山不崩解陵不阤<span class='krp-note'>案阤/各本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='6975:7014'><span class='krp-note'>作施下又衍谷/字今從方本</span>川谷不處<span class='krp-note'>案谷各本訛作/浴今從方本</span>深淵不涸于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='7014:7041'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '009-15b' );" name="009-15b" class="pb">[009-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='7041:7064'>時龍至不閉鳯降忘翼鷙獸忘攫爪鳥忘距䗦蠆不螫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='7064:7087'>嬰兒蟁䖟不食夭駒雒出服河出圖自上世以來莫不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='7087:7110'>降仁國家之昌國家之臧信仁是故不賞不罰而民咸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='7110:7142'>盡力<span class='krp-note'>案而各本作/如今從方本</span>車不建戈遠邇咸服𦙍使來往地濱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='7142:7173'>畢極<span class='krp-note'>案濱各本訛作/賓今從方本</span>無怨無惡率惟懿徳此無空禮無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='7173:7196'>空名賢人竝優殘毒以時省舉良良舉善善恤民使仁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='7196:7217'>日斆仁賓<span class='krp-note'>案此下各本有/也字今從楊本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='7217:7226'>　大戴禮記卷九</span><br/>
